{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"七彩笔  为迎接第三个五年计划作","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":1,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为迎接第三个五年计划作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新天地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘天梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手是党解放的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤胆是党染红的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山当马任我骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海当瓢任我提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的年月映赤旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆大寨啊传奇迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手就是金钥匙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再为大地取新衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春应当献给你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，社会主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命应当捍卫你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最英勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看刀在豺狼颈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上红云挤乌云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说和野兽能共处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说宁肯“人类再生”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造一座红色楼台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下战友同歌吟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色山水红梅岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝枝争作万年春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手拔山啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义新愚公。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤当当啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高奏时代最强音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山擂鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹号——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄桥上一声唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天南海北伴你笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄桥上一声笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里风云手上招。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要攀险峰请架桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要劈高山请点炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利消息似雪片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顷刻化作大江潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义你敢挡道？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这炮声你挡不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级敌人你敢嘲笑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这笑声你压不倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声声——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“唱得一禾生九穗”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中冉冉太阳升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“唱得春风笑开口”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火熊熊钢铁鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗下走来新一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如花似火正年青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛骇浪里头不回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹浪打啊见红心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我们高吹革命号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出满天红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我们歌唱毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做宇宙的主人翁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新天地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘天梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天梯通往哪里去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步攀向高峰去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩笔写下火焰诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让世界有奴隶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际高歌歌一曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江东去浪万里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯月变桥啊星变花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶的镣铐铸金犁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级亿万兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生是武器；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧，明天的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定是共产主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年冬天作"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}